title: Night's Watch vs Wildlings: Battle for the Wall - Seven Kingdoms Total War Mod Gameplay
description:
The Wall is under siege!  The Wildlings have gathered a mighty force to conquer the wall and harass the southern lands of Westeros.  Jon Snow leads a desperate defense with his fellow Night Brothers.  Enjoy the Battle :D

Seven Kingdoms Total War is a mod for Total War: Attila
